    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p>
        We believe in sharing our work with the world. The complete source code for <strong>"Minister of Truth"</strong> is available on
        <a href="https://github.com/borissedov/GGJ2025" target="_blank">GitHub</a>. Feel free to explore, contribute, or use it as inspiration
        for your own projects!
    </p>

    <p>
        Created during an exhilarating 48-hour jam, <strong>"Minister of Truth"</strong> blends humor, strategy, and satire to deliver a
        unique gaming experience. By leveraging the theme of "Bubbles," we aim to entertain while sparking conversations about
        the nature of influence and the narratives we believe.
    </p>

    <p>
        We hope you enjoy playing our game as much as we enjoyed creating it!
